{"tid":2401864,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"買過GME SH過既入一入黎","createTime":"2021-02-10T05:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T15:11:39.000Z","uid":107157,"like":51,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"775206d363ab36bc5868eb855a150dd5bec51c4c","tid":2401864,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:11:24.000Z","msg":"關注他 追看他 在螢幕裡牽掛 <br />\n升距被限制嗎 不必怕 <br />\nibank 隔絕我跟他 封鎖了嗎 便跌下 <br />\n<br />\n十四天 大概足以證實 情商你會自理<br />\n何以 資訊消失 不再說起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da696e29b374712ff3de275a457bf558ac19073","tid":2401864,"uid":22309,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:12:23.000Z","msg":"智商我會自理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df10dfb1129c6f9d9015bad72778dc24cb3abed4","tid":2401864,"uid":148447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84954e167cfb6d47a921493ddc64d7585d679a9","tid":2401864,"uid":104865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"殘局也要試　還沒有算輸　很專注<br />\n我尚在為我的結局　再試試<br />\n我知　想扭轉弱勢　都不易<br />\n<br />\n誰話我介意　誰話我怕輸<br />\n真諷刺　我若是做到收放自如<br />\n為何仍和你對峙<br />\n<br />\n一錯手　這盤棋也許已捉到盡頭<br />\n我知　我的棋藝仍然未夠<br />\n攻與守　被你牽著我走　與你鬥　那夠你鬥<br />\n但願　若拚死搶救　棋逢敵手<br />\n<br />\n一敗塗地　一絲生機<br />\n一場歡喜　一幕好戲<br />\n一段緣分　興衰生死　從此交給你<br />\n共你相依到死　或要分離　就看你下這顆棋<br />\n結果　誰人才是皺著眉<br />\n<br />\n還沒到最尾　還剩兩隻棋<br />\n一口氣　我若未認輸　舉了白旗<br />\n懸崖前　仍要競技<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets